# <%= mod %>

A Dialup web application.

## Getting Started

To start your Dialup application:

```bash
mix deps.get
mix run --no-halt
```

Then visit [`http://localhost:4000`](http://localhost:4000).

## Project Structure

```
lib/
├── <%= app %>.ex          # Application module
└── app/
    ├── layout.ex          # Root layout
    └── page.ex            # Home page at /
```

